Commands available in TEXT mode:

   cl_ear               - clear buffer, deleting any text entered
   e_dit                - invoke editor
   h_elp [<topic> ... ] - get more info on something
   ok                   - end text entry and prompt for verification
   p_rint               - reprint text
   q_uit                - abort text entry
   r_ead <filename>     - append file contents to the buffer
   w_rite <filename>    - write buffer out to a disk file
